data.title: Web Call LTR Chsl-2016
data.meta_description: Web Call Ltr Chsl-2016 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document provides a list of 63 candidates who have been scheduled for a Document Verification (DV) and Data Entry Speed Test (DEST)/Typing Test between November 27, 2017 and December 19, 2017 as part of the Combined Higher Secondary Level (10+2) Examination, 2016. It includes each candidate's roll number, name, date of DV, reporting time for DV, date of skill test, batch number and reporting time for the skill test. Candidates are advised to familiarize themselves with instructions available on the Commission's website and ensure they meet all eligibility criteria.
